.SH "NAME"
clx \- Hacker News in your terminal
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.sp
\fBclx\fP [\fIOPTION\fP].\|.\|.
.sp
\fBclx\fP \fICOMMAND\fP [\fIARGS\fP]
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.sp
\fBcircumflex\fP lets you browse Hacker News in your terminal.
Visit the comment section or read the article in Reader Mode.
.SH "KEYBINDINGS"
.sp
\fIEnter\fP
.RS 4
Read the comment section.
.RE
.sp
\fISpace\fP
.RS 4
Read the article in Reader Mode.
.RE
.sp
\fIr\fP
.RS 4
Re\-fetch submissions for the current category.
.RE
.sp
\fITab\fP
.RS 4
Change category (use Shift + Tab to change in opposite direction).
.RE
.sp
\fIo\fP
.RS 4
Open link to article in browser.
See \fBCLX_BROWSER\fP.
.RE
.sp
\fIc\fP
.RS 4
Open comment section in browser.
.RE
.sp
\fIf\fP, \fIV\fP
.RS 4
Add currently highlighted submission to favorites.
.RE
.sp
\fIx\fP
.RS 4
Remove currently highlighted submission from favorites.
.RE
.sp
\fIu\fP
.RS 4
Toggle read/unread for the currently highlighted submission.
.RE
.sp
\fIj\fP, \fIk\fP
.RS 4
Move down/up one item.
.RE
.sp
\fIh\fP, \fIl\fP
.RS 4
Previous/next page.
.RE
.sp
\fIg\fP, \fIG\fP
.RS 4
Go to the top/bottom of the list.
.RE
.sp
\fIi\fP, \fI?\fP
.RS 4
Bring up the help screen.
.RE
.sp
\fIq\fP, \fIEsc\fP
.RS 4
Quit to prompt.
.RE
.SH "COMMENT SECTION"
.sp
The comment section has two interaction modes, toggled with \fITab\fP.
.SS "Read Mode"
.sp
The default mode.
Scroll through the comment section line by line.
.sp
\fIj\fP, \fIk\fP
.RS 4
Scroll down/up one line.
.RE
.sp
\fId\fP, \fIu\fP
.RS 4
Scroll down/up half a page.
.RE
.sp
\fISpace\fP/\fIf\fP, \fIb\fP
.RS 4
Page down/up.
.RE
.sp
\fIg\fP, \fIG\fP
.RS 4
Go to top/bottom.
.RE
.sp
\fIn\fP, \fIN\fP
.RS 4
Jump to next/previous top\-level comment.
.RE
.sp
\fIh\fP, \fIl\fP
.RS 4
Collapse/expand one level.
.RE
.sp
\fIo\fP
.RS 4
Open link to article in browser.
.RE
.sp
\fIc\fP
.RS 4
Open comment section in browser.
.RE
.sp
\fIEnter\fP
.RS 4
Toggle collapse all.
.RE
.sp
\fITab\fP
.RS 4
Switch to navigate mode.
.RE
.sp
\fIi\fP, \fI?\fP
.RS 4
Bring up the help screen.
.RE
.sp
\fIq\fP, \fIEsc\fP
.RS 4
Go back.
.RE
